bgm.name: オーケストラ・奇妙な感じ・やや暗い・展開がある

parameters:
\n<Lyric>"We've arrived. This is the place, right here. Where you all
were captured."

\n<Roselitte>"It's quite a deep location... Indeed, jumping into the
river at that time might have been the right decision."
Saying that, Roselitte placed her hand on Lyric's head.
\n<Ameria>"Muu... Roselitte-san and Lyric are so close..."
